n your résumé. These tools and techniques all help accomplish one common goal: being able to increase sales for your brand. If you're committed to being at the top of your career game, the Complete Digital Marketing Growth Hacking Certification Bundle can get you up to speed and it will only cost you $34.99. \nThis nine-part course is taught by some of the best in the business. Entrepreneur and marketing innovator Benjamin Wilson will kick things off, and later, marketing creative Matt Jensen is set to take charge along with a number of other top-rated instructors.\nIn total, the bundle features 41 hours of marketing lessons on Facebook, YouTube, Google, Amazon, and more. First up, you'll begin with the Certified Facebook Marketing 2020 lesson, which offers a step-by-step guide to simple strategies for gaining targeted followers that will eventually lead to sales. Next, you'll move onto a crash course on Google Tag Manager that covers its importance and exactly how to use it. \nPerhaps the most essential course is the Complete Growth Hacking and Conversion Course, which covers everything from optimizing CTAs to retargeting interested shoppers. If you're serious about truly growing your online presence, you'll need to take note of these strategies.\nIf you already know what strategies and platforms you want to target first, you may choose to skip around and tackle the Go Viral on YouTube hour-long lecture or the SEO link building course. There is even a full course on Pinterest marketing.\nFinally, the Amazon FBA closes out the course package by outlining how you can start a business utilizing Amazon's tools and make it successful — which many sellers fail to do. \nWith nine courses in total, it's no surprise that this bundle is worth over a grand in value. But you can go after your marketing dreams and snag access for just $34.99.\n\n            \n              \n                \n              \n            \n            \n              The Complete Digital Marketing Growth Hacking Certification Bundle — $34.99\n              See Details"},"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fcard%252Fimage%252F1438591%252F2e98f27b-261b-4152-a45f-5101b2f7f193.jpeg%252F950x534__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpeg?signature=YgxMsoXD3HQXRWcFfZc27iGjvvQ=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","feature_image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F117829%252F076e66bb-de78-4b6b-85d3-14bdc3b7a7da.jpeg%252F1438x0.jpeg?signature=tNDgnsVPMC66LFvG9ve9XsqCBOw=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","responsive_images":[{"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F117829%252F076e66bb-de78-4b6b-85d3-14bdc3b7a7da.jpeg%252F356x205.jpeg?signature=XRVRSot9pmpM6kJ_z-FP-BybCFI=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","query":true,"size":"356x205#"},{"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F117829%252F076e66bb-de78-4b6b-85d3-14bdc3b7a7da.jpeg%252F712x410.jpeg?signature=wIe7FEuRTUwcsd3C-CoFQEbaoUk=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","query":"(min-resolution: 1.5dppx)","size":"712x410#"},{"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F117829%252F076e66bb-de78-4b6b-85d3-14bdc3b7a7da.jpeg%252F280x157.jpeg?signature=sNzbf_aWmUASqcOuhtafG_1atq0=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","query":"(max-width: 480px)","size":"280x157#"},{"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F117829%252F076e66bb-de78-4b6b-85d3-14bdc3b7a7da.jpeg%252F560x314.jpeg?signature=X2P8kfyR5-BALKHXDJlchpBv8xA=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","query":"(max-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 1.5dppx)","size":"560x314#"}],"responsive_images_html5":{"img_set_info":{"tag_attributes":{"class":"microcontent","alt":"This marketing course bundle will teach you how to increase everythin